data.description: Nestled in the lively Tartesso, this home presents a harmonious blend of comfort and modern living. You'll be greeted by an inviting living room adorned with vaulted ceilings, plush carpet, and abundant natural light. The modern eat-in kitchen boasts pristine quartz counters, paneled cabinets, SS appliances, a pantry, and a serving window with a breakfast bar. The spacious main bedroom offers an ensuite with dual sinks and for added convenience. Venture outside to a meticulously designed backyard featuring a covered patio, low-maintenance artificial turf, and a stylish pergola - an ideal spot for relaxation. The Community includes many amenities including sports courts, refreshing splash pads, and picturesque parks. Make it yours!
